title: The Anti-Christ - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 5/20/22
itunes:title: The Anti-Christ - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 5/20/22
description:
Guest host Ian Punnett and a pair of open line callers debate possible candidates for the Anti-Christ, and how symbols in the Bible that forecast when he will arrive can be misinterpreted.
